donorname: Eurasian Fund for Stabilization and Development
agencyname: Eurasian Fund for Stabilization and Development
projecttitle: Irrigation System Modernization Project in Armenia
project_descrip: Short: IRRIGATION SYSTEM MODERNIZATION PROJECT IN ARMENIA Long: The project is part of the long-term national programme to restore and restructure the irrigation and drainage network in Armenia. The Project involves construction of canals in different regions of Armenia: the sites selected for the Project include those where the need for investment is most acute.
